strings.Value: "I've always believed that everyone carries an animal inside. Now I see these animals struggling to come out."
"I hope you don't see it as a philosophical problem. Obviously, we're dealing with some evil magic here, and we'll have to remember that when we confront it."
"The animal inside? You may be right about that, but what we're fighting now is not some inner monster of the soul."
"Hah. Like the butterfly from its cocoon."
"Would be awesome if greatbeast was inside Nok-Nok. But maybe not come out yet. Nok-Nok still have plans..."
"In order for a monster to break out, it needs to have been put inside in the first place."
"In order for a monster to break out, it needs to have been put inside in the first place."
